WEBVTT

00:07.921 --> 00:10.788
- Hi, everybody.
- Hi, Carla.

00:10.962 --> 00:13.332
Sam, l'm sorry l'm late.

00:13.504 --> 00:16.667
l realise l left you here
without a waitress.

00:18.378 --> 00:20.416
What am l? Chopped liver?

00:20.587 --> 00:23.419
No, some people enjoy chopped liver.

00:25.878 --> 00:30.167
- What got you in such a bad mood?
- l don't know. Everything.

00:30.336 --> 00:35.372
This morning l was thinking l'm not
married, l'm carrying my sixth kid.

00:35.544 --> 00:38.210
l'm broke, l live in squalor...

00:39.835 --> 00:43.201
- l'm having a crisis of faith.
- Don't talk like that.

00:43.376 --> 00:46.707
Would a just God
be putting me through this?

00:46.876 --> 00:50.241
Well, l know it looks
sort of bleak out there.

00:50.417 --> 00:53.534
But you just have to have patience.
Remember Job.

00:53.709 --> 00:57.749
Cliffie's right, honey.
You got a good Job here.

01:00.292 --> 01:04.037
- You're in great health...
- l don't know.

01:05.875 --> 01:08.789
l didn't want to embarrass you
in front of Carla,

01:08.958 --> 01:11.956
but you pronounce the word ''job''.

